[{"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T22:07:29+00:00", "description": "<p>In our <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/oneplus-12-review-a-no-nonsense-flagship-for-a-great-price-180050960.html\">review</a> of the <a data-i13n=\"elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAASKd37oxLd", "id": 1283808, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/the-oneplus-12-smartphone-drops-to-a-record-low-of-650-for-prime-day-220729473.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F9aa42630-c5dc-11ee-bfff-8b57c65d8206&resize=1400%2C840&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=b08e0e7a1b1a695bdfa380f6404f215a451935cc", "title": "The OnePlus 12 smartphone drops to a record low of $650 for Prime Day", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T21:00:14+00:00", "description": "<p>Amazon Prime Big Deal Days is back this year, returning on <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/deals/amazon-announces-the-return-of-prime-big-deal-days-on-october-8-and-9-050356758.html\">October 8 and 9</a>. The \u201cfall <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/\">Prime Day</a>\u201d of sorts has served as the online retailer\u2019s unofficial kickoff to the holiday shopping season for the past few years. We expect most of the deals to be Prime exclusives, meaning you must be an active Prime subscriber to get the discounts. There are always a couple of deals available for everyone, though, so it\u2019s worth perusing Amazon\u2019s site even if you don\u2019t pay for Prime. It\u2019s also worth doing so now because we\u2019ve found a number of solid early Prime Day deals already available. These are the best of the bunch; we\u2019ll be updating this post regularly in the lead-up to October Prime Day, so check back for the latest deals.</p>\n<h2 id=\"jump-link-prime-day-d", "id": 1283410, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day-deals-are-available-to-shop-before-october-big-deal-days-starts-tomorrow-190039152.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F0be3dbb0-2ff5-11ef-bbf1-7d96d6a22ddb&resize=1400%2C787&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=cb2495afe25559e14d427f0f1f9345e523e3c6ed", "title": "Amazon Prime Day deals are available to shop before October Big Deal Days starts tomorrow", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T19:29:58+00:00", "description": "<p><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/\">October Prime Day</a> is nearly here, but we're seeing more new deals pop up in the final hours before the event kicks off. One of the best laptop deals we're seeing at the moment is on <a data-i13n=\"elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZB37iOrcaxOco9US9bR2rUNPpyb08F7_Fd6", "id": 1283003, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/prime-day-deals-on-laptops-include-the-m2-macbook-air-for-a-record-low-of-749-on-amazon-121848095.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2022-11%2F2cf20390-5a13-11ed-af3f-7a2131510b1f&resize=1400%2C840&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=ca295f383b82ef3da2427a019047a5746d3d510b", "title": "Prime Day deals on laptops include the M2 MacBook Air for a record low of $749 on Amazon", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T18:45:54+00:00", "description": "<p>Comcast is warning that hackers stole the personal data of more than 230,000 customers during a ransomware attack on a third-party debt collector, <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.maine.gov/agviewer/content/ag/985235c7-cb95-4be2-8792-a1252b4f8318/aff9fd91-81e8-4d95-a84e-c56f1d48f088.html?7194ef805fa2d04b0f7e8c9521f97343\">according to a court filing</a>. The bad actors targeted a Pennsylvania-based debt collection agency called Financial Business and Consumer Solutions (FBCS.)</p>\n<p>The attack occurred back in February, but Comcast claims that FBCS initially said that the incident didn\u2019t involve any customer data. FBCS changed its tune by July, when it notified Comcast that customer information had been compromised, <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://techcrunch.com/2024/10/07/comcast-says-customer-data-stolen-in-ransomware-attack-on-debt-collection-agency/\">according to reporting by <em>TechCrunch</em></a>.</p>\n<span id=\"end-legacy-contents\"></span><p>All told, ", "id": 1282638, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/cybersecurity/comcast-says-230000-customers-affected-by-debt-collection-data-breach-184554728.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2Fd3fcdf40-84d5-11ef-b3f9-9c3251b44993&resize=1400%2C722&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=ea2a4ce2c82d6cb80ae9b39f14cd2d44c119adff", "title": "Comcast says 230,000 customers affected by debt collection data breach", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T18:36:17+00:00", "description": "<p>Twitch is striving for more clarity about why and how it executes its policies. On Monday, the company <a data-i13n=\"elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1\" class=\"no-affiliate-link\" href=\"https://x.com/TwitchSupport/status/1843331493466141071\" data-original-link=\"https://x.com/TwitchSupport/status/1843331493466141071\">said</a> it\u2019s adding Enforcement Notes, which it describes as \u201cadditional clarifications and examples within the Community Guidelines designed to make our rules easier to follow.\u201d The notes come on the heels of (and complement) the company\u2019s recent promise that it would <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/entertainment/streaming/twitch-will-do-a-better-job-of-telling-rulebreakers-why-their-accounts-were-suspended-191502111.html\">do a better job of telling rule-breakers</a> why their accounts were suspended.</p>\n<p>The company says Enforcement Notes will outline how its rules apply to the trends you see on the platform. For example, i", "id": 1282639, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/social-media/twitch-makes-its-complicated-rulebook-easier-to-follow-183617108.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2Ffdc361d0-84d7-11ef-83df-66abf930898c&resize=1400%2C788&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=b65d90a702c917e8aa2181ad3500d3c16421df0a", "title": "Twitch makes its complicated rulebook easier to follow", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T17:40:16+00:00", "description": "<p>Nintendo\u2019s new Switch bundles are here. As the seven-year-old console takes its victory lap ahead of the Switch 2, the <a data-i13n=\"elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Walmart;elmt:;cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=3719d8d4-5edd-4817-998a-91f3229e7323&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Walmart&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy53YWxtYXJ0LmNvbS9pcC9IQURTS0FCU0IvMTEzNjY5Njk3NDg_Y2xhc3NUeXBlPVJFR1VMQVImYXRoYmRnPUwxNjAwJmZyb209L3NlYXJjaCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMWU0YTg1ZTQtODkyMy00MDBlLWJhMzktYjQzNWEyYzAwODNmIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy53YWxtYXJ0LmNvbS9pcC9IQURTS0FCU0IvMTEzNjY5Njk3NDg_Y2xhc3NUeXBlPVJFR1VMQVImYXRoYmRnPUwxNjAwJmZyb209L3NlYXJjaCJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAfW68uQAxyf4AGJQaKa4EnxQ6ldWwlIHFwPLWHakcZVw&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.walmart.com%2Fip%2FHADSKABSB%2F11366969748%3FclassType%3DREGULAR%26athbdg%3DL1600%26from%3D%2Fsearch\" class=\"", "id": 1282174, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/gaming/nintendo/nintendos-discounted-switch-bundles-are-now-available-174016292.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2F9e150cc0-84c8-11ef-be0b-4c4402bbfb82&resize=1400%2C933&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=529281a4ca9915f8bd48f539dcd5aac81fa7ecb5", "title": "Nintendo\u2019s discounted Switch bundles are now available", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T17:31:35+00:00", "description": "<p>If you\u2019re active on Meta\u2019s Threads app, then you\u2019ve probably encountered some amount of engagement bait in your \u201cfor you\u201d\u201d feed. Now, Instagram chief Adam Mosseri has acknowledged the issue, saying that the company is \u201cworking to get it under control\" after a spike in such posts.</p>\n<p>\u201cWe\u2019ve seen an increase in engagement-bait on Threads and we\u2019re working to get it under control,\u201d Mosseri said in <a data-i13n=\"elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1\" class=\"no-affiliate-link\" href=\"https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA01Sd8vtm6\" data-original-link=\"https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA01Sd8vtm6\">a post</a> on Threads. He didn\u2019t say what steps the company is taking but said there would be \u201cmore to come\u201d on the issue.</p>\n<span id=\"end-legacy-contents\"></span><p>Mosseri\u2019s comments are the first time the Meta executive has acknowledged the problem that\u2019s become an increasingly prominent topic of discussion on Threads. Because the app defaults to the algorithmic \u201cfor ", "id": 1282175, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/social-media/meta-is-working-to-fix-threads-engagement-bait-problem-173135011.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2F02a18050-84cf-11ef-bfe7-41b026093654&resize=1400%2C845&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=da998ca331a3312e48f2177f0e38e93b3d54a7c1", "title": "Meta is working to fix Threads' engagement bait problem", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T17:20:10+00:00", "description": "<p><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/\"><ins>Prime Day</ins></a> is back, meaning there are a ton of deals worth checking out on Amazon. Those who have been looking for a robot vacuum cleaner are in luck, as there are deals on several of iRobot's Roomba devices. The Combo j9+, which also includes a mop function, has <a data-i13n=\"elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzQxNUhRUFg_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy0yMCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiNjZkNDYwZDItMWM4Yi00OTEwLWFmNGEtOWEzNjZiN2Q3ZTNlIiwib3JpZ2luYWxVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5hbWF6b24uY29tL2RwL0IwQzQxNUhRUFgiLCJkeW5hbWljQ2VudHJhbFRyYWNraW5nSWQiOnRydWUsInNpdGVJZCI6InVzLWVuZ2FkZ2V0IiwicGFnZUlkIjoiMXAtYXV0b2xpbms", "id": 1282176, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/irobots-roomba-combo-j9-robot-vacuum-and-mop-is-600-off-for-prime-day-172009289.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2F0e7e0770-84cc-11ef-be7d-81f795f273a9&resize=1400%2C787&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=857f5ccea469a7f5d36184074bf2b801d2a38a6a", "title": "iRobot's Roomba Combo j9+ robot vacuum and mop is $600 off for Prime Day", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T16:51:37+00:00", "description": "<p>The EA/Codemasters racing sim <em>Grid Legends</em> is coming to mobile this December, after first <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/grid-legends-release-date-codemasters-ea-210519482.html\"><ins>releasing for consoles and PC back in 2022</ins></a>. It\u2019s actually a port of the deluxe edition of the game, which was originally released in 2023. This version includes all of the available DLC and some other goodies.</p>\n<p>It\u2019s coming to iOS and Android and offers \u201cfull support for all popular gamepads\u201d, with touch and tilt controls for those who don\u2019t have a third-party gamepad. There\u2019s a trailer, with footage captured on mobile devices, and it looks pretty darn good. The visuals are, dare I say, console-worthy.</p>\n<span id=\"end-legacy-contents\"></span><div id=\"2d5623f656544507aa30e8ba36b23871\"><iframe width=\"560\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/LqkY01avl-Q?si=5hUy54WjJ3y9gmv5\" title=\"YouTube video player\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\"></i", "id": 1281702, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/gaming/eas-grid-legends-racing-game-careens-onto-ios-and-android-this-december-165137002.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2Fd9ecfc40-84c7-11ef-96ed-11b465d618d4&resize=1400%2C787&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=6a9cd3ff7967d0bbe38b61665efad90ad3056f6a", "title": "EA's Grid Legends racing game careens onto iOS and Android this December", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T16:22:14+00:00", "description": "<p>Many fans of 2014\u2019s <em>Alien: Isolation</em> video game praised its graphics, story and general gameplay, making it a bit of a standout from many other games adapted from a movie. It even received seven separate DLC packs. Gamers have been enjoying this cult classic on <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/alien-isolation-ios-android-release-date-163249099.html?_fsig=Wkc.MxMszdLZVqSCzBon_g--%7EA\"><ins>mobile</ins></a> and <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/2019-06-11-alien-isolation-for-switch.html\"><ins>Switch</ins></a> for a while now, but today, on the game\u2019s 10th anniversary, the developers announced that they\u2019re developing a sequel.</p>\n<p>Yes, you heard us right. <em>Alien: Isolation</em> now has a sequel in early development. If you don\u2019t believe us, take the <a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://x.com/AlienIsolation/status/1843305291322200488\">official X account\u2019s word</a> for it.</p>\n<span id=\"end-legacy-contents\"></span><p", "id": 1281703, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/gaming/pc/sequel-to-2014s-alien-isolation-is-now-in-development-162213148.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2F27618160-84c5-11ef-bdf3-514a18caeaae&resize=1400%2C787&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=f664216ad7e79b804015456812a89babcef9da2d", "title": "Sequel to 2014\u2019s Alien: Isolation is now in development", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T15:35:13+00:00", "description": "<p><a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/\"><ins>Prime Day</ins></a> is almost upon us, but you don't have to wait any time at all to find some good deals. Case in point: both variants of the PS5 Slim have dropped by $50, so if you've been holding off on making the leap to <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/best-gaming-console-140057674.html\"><ins>current-gen consoles</ins></a> (and the <a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/gaming/playstation/sony-unveils-its-ps5-pro-console-which-will-cost-you-a-whopping-700-151636487.html\"><ins>PS5 Pro</ins></a> is perhaps a little too on the pricey side), this is a solid discount that's worth considering. The Digital Edition (the one without a disc drive) has <a data-i13n=\"elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:4;pos:1\" href=\"https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureI", "id": 1281074, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/ps5-slim-consoles-are-50-off-ahead-of-prime-day-153513934.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://