merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAfFGfsLrMP01ZsJ4DzDPbFuU6hVZ4Zlo6RmMCcM-3PoA&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fstores%2Fpage%2F1B272CDD-6230-40E0-8E10-52C64B25CE49\" class=\"rapid-with-clickid\" data-original-link=\"https://www.amazo", "id": 1280515, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/deals/prime-day-starts-tomorrow-and-the-ring-pan-tilt-indoor-cam-is-already-on-sale-for-a-record-low-of-50-144458370.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-04%2F1a622dd0-06d4-11ef-bfbf-18df87a77781&resize=1400%2C910&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=b11105c81bed557ea90d2439fae6567c2778dd91", "title": "Prime Day starts tomorrow and the Ring Pan-Tilt indoor Cam is already on sale for a record-low of $50", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T12:27:38+00:00", "description": "<p>With <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/amazon-prime-day/\">October Prime Day</a> approaching fast, we're seeing new deals drop in the final hours of the lead up. One of the latest deals is on the <a data-i13n=\"elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:;cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAZB37iOrcaxOco9US9bR2rUNPpyb08F7_Fd6lUDlSr5J&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.am", "id": 1279861, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/prime-day-apple-deals-include-the-m2-macbook-air-for-a-record-low-of-749-121848970.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2022-11%2F2cf20390-5a13-11ed-af3f-7a2131510b1f&resize=1400%2C840&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=ca295f383b82ef3da2427a019047a5746d3d510b", "title": "Prime Day Apple deals include the M2 MacBook Air for a record low of $749", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T12:00:41+00:00", "description": "<p>At yesterday&#39;s Halo World Championships, developer 343 Industries <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.halowaypoint.com/news/a-new-dawn\">announced</a> that it was officially changing its name to Halo Studios. The company also revealed that it has multiple new games in the pipeline and is switching all future Halo development from its proprietary Slipspace Engine to <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/unreal-engine-5-available-release-date-151023130.html\">Unreal Engine 5</a>.&nbsp;</p>\n<p>In a YouTube video (below) the new studio showed elements from the &quot;Project Foundry&quot; Unreal Engine research effort that has been ongoing for the past several years. While just a tech demo for now, it showed Master Chief and Covenant elite designs, along with three biomes including a Cascades-type location, Flood-impacted Blightlands and snowy Coldlands.&nbsp;</p>\n<span id=\"end-legacy-contents\"></span><div id=\"97312ace65614d4fbd3ade4e0840017a\"><div style", "id": 1279862, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/gaming/halo-developer-343-industries-rebrands-itself-to-halo-studios-120041943.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2F949a9120-8481-11ef-a9f5-92a8cbff301b&resize=1400%2C787&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=9661fa0ad5bc3f16e7c8372915c95bfe5e02ddbc", "title": "'Halo' developer 343 Industries rebrands itself to Halo Studios", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T12:00:29+00:00", "description": "<p>Playing <em>Phoenix Springs</em> feels like being trapped in a gorgeous dream that\u2019s steadily becoming a nightmare. It\u2019s a point-and-click mystery set in a bleak futuristic world of dramatic shadows and muted primary colors, its scenes connected by streams of anxious static. The game stars Iris Dormer, a technology reporter who\u2019s searching for her estranged brother, Leo. Her hunt takes her from the abandoned buildings of a rundown city, to a rich suburb, and finally to Phoenix Springs, a desert oasis bathed in golden light and occupied by a handful of odd, disconnected people.</p> \n<p>Iris is the heart of <em>Phoenix Springs</em>. She narrates the on-screen action in a stoic, unaffected tone that belies the cutting poetry of her observations. Iris has just three options when interacting with people and items: talk to, look at or use. Relevant concepts and objects are collected in her mental inventory, a simple word cloud of black text on a white background. Open the inventory with ", "id": 1279863, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/gaming/pc/phoenix-springs-review-a-dazzling-and-disquieting-sci-fi-mystery-120029156.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-10%2Fe8a40c50-8450-11ef-bf22-f5c78be2bbaf&resize=1400%2C787&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=57ae4bdafab1e43f96e6cd1c216d57ba8b6c02d3", "title": "Phoenix Springs review: A dazzling and disquieting sci-fi mystery", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T11:15:44+00:00", "description": "<p>It&#39;s been a wait. Apple Intelligence will start <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/ai/the-first-apple-intelligence-features-are-expected-to-arrive-on-october-28-144459627.html\">rolling out</a> on October 28, according to <em>Bloomberg</em>\u2019s Mark Gurman. Apple said last month it was targeting October for iOS 18.1, iPadOS 18.1, and macOS Sequoia 15.1 \u2014 which will bring some of the first Apple Intelligence features to iPhone 16 and the rest of the Apple family.</p>\n<p>The first wave of Apple Intelligence-powered features will include its summarization tool, Writing Tools and smart audio recording and transcriptions for Mail, Notes, Pages and other apps. I\u2019ve been testing the beta, and so far, the most useful feature has been the summarization tool, tackling my forest of notifications and messages and parsing them into glanceable summaries.</p>\n<p>\u2014 Mat Smith</p>\n<p><strong>The biggest stories you might have missed</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><p><a data-i13n=\"cpo", "id": 1279405, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/general/the-morning-after-the-first-apple-intelligence-features-should-finally-arrive-on-october-28-111544744.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-06%2F9bae8bf0-2771-11ef-b9f5-387c61a085e6&resize=1400%2C786&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=0167ce35e190dc6a11964cac3f20c500db45a049", "title": "The Morning After: The first Apple Intelligence features should finally arrive on October 28", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T09:00:36+00:00", "description": "<p>A lot of people started to care about \u201chigh resolution\u201d digital audio when Apple launched its <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/apple-music-lossless-now-available-on-supported-devices-094540982.html\">upgraded music service</a> to the masses. Call that the \u201cApple effect,\u201d as infuriating as it may be, but the iPhone maker isn\u2019t the only one in the hi-res audio game: <a data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/2019-11-11-qobuz-drops-lossy-music-streaming.html\">Qobuz</a>, <a data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/2019-12-12-tidal-hifi-dolby-atmos-music.html\">Tidal</a> and <a data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/2019-11-18-deezer-hifi-on-mobile-and-web.html\">Deezer</a> have been doing it for a while, and <a data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/spotify-hifi-select-markets-premium-cd-quality-audio-2021-165438547.html\">Spotify</a> has been toying with releasing its own version for a while. Howeve", "id": 1278660, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/the-best-dac-for-lossless-high-resolution-music-iphone-android-160056147.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-02%2F537f5250-d4bb-11ee-bdcf-b2057716deaf&resize=1400%2C787&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=cdf4445d90b5217f45b2a6e946a68848343fb71d", "title": "The best DACs for Apple Music Lossless in 2024", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-07T07:00:36+00:00", "description": "<p>Choosing the best portable speaker can be a daunting task with the amount of options available today. Whether you're gearing up for a camping trip, a beach outing, or a backyard barbecue, finding the right speaker that delivers on sound quality, durability, and portability is crucial. We've tested dozens of Bluetooth speakers across various price points to help you navigate this crowded market. While many of them sound impressive, comparing them head-to-head allowed us to identify the features that make certain portable wireless speakers stand out.<br><br>If you\u2019re looking primarily for a speaker that works with a voice assistant like Alexa, Google Assistant or Siri, check out our top picks for the <a data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" href=\"https://www.engadget.com/best-smart-speakers-151515264.html\">best smart speaker</a>s. However, for those seeking a versatile portable Bluetooth speaker, we've put together a selection of top performers that cater to a wide range of use cases and preferen", "id": 1278206, "language": "en-US", "link": "https://www.engadget.com/audio/speakers/best-portable-bluetooth-speakers-133004551.html?src=rss", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 86, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 104, "source_url": "https://www.engadget.com/rss.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": "https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2024-04%2F7373a7a0-f739-11ee-b9f7-4be4e47294ab&resize=1400%2C787&client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&signature=fcfc09f21728db914eea82f811d54b518956acb7", "title": "The best Bluetooth speaker for 2024: 17 portable options for every price range", "vote": 0}]